===============================================================================

Component Information
===============================================================================

Component: openjornada-webapp
- openjornada-admin: Admin Panel (Next.js)
- openjornada-webapp: Worker Web App (React + Vite)
- openjornada-landing: Landing Page
- openjornada-saas-portal: SaaS Registration Portal

Language: TypeScript/JavaScript
Framework: React / Next.js / Vite

This component provides the user interface for OpenJornada's time tracking system.

