Network Use Provision (AGPL-3.0 Specific)
===============================================================================

If you run a modified version of this application on a server and let other
users access it through a network, your server must also allow them to
download the source code corresponding to the modified version running there.

This means that if you use this component as part of a SaaS offering, you must
provide access to the source code, including any modifications you have made.

