Third-Party Dependencies (Frontend)
===============================================================================

This component includes or depends on the following open-source libraries:

Core Framework:
- React (18.2.0) - MIT License
  https://github.com/facebook/react
- Next.js (14.0.0) - MIT License (for Admin/Portal)
  https://github.com/vercel/next.js
- Vite (5.0.0) - MIT License (for Webapp/Landing)
  https://github.com/vitejs/vite

TypeScript:
- TypeScript (5.3.2) - Apache License 2.0
  https://github.com/microsoft/TypeScript

Styling:
- Tailwind CSS (3.3.5) - MIT License
  https://github.com/tailwindlabs/tailwindcss
- PostCSS (8.4.31) - MIT License
  https://github.com/postcss/postcss

HTTP Client:
- Axios (1.6.0) - MIT License
  https://github.com/axios/axios

UI Components & Utilities:
- React Hot Toast (2.4.1) - MIT License
  https://github.com/timolins/react-hot-toast
- React Icons (4.11.0) - MIT License
  https://github.com/react-icons/react-icons
- Lucide React (0.292.0) - ISC License
  https://github.com/lucide-icons/lucide

Routing:
- React Router DOM (6.18.0) - MIT License (for Vite apps)
  https://github.com/remix-run/react-router

Build Tools:
- ESLint (8.53.0) - MIT License
  https://github.com/eslint/eslint
- Prettier (3.1.0) - MIT License (if used)
  https://github.com/prettier/prettier

All third-party licenses are compatible with AGPL-3.0 and are included
in their respective dependency packages.

